title: Black Keys - The Big Come Up - FLAC
description:
This is the debut album from the Black Keys.

Thanks to obmen for the original release of this in WMA Lossless. I am re-upping it in FLAC for those that prefer this format like I do. It didn&#039;t come with any documentation or log files but I had a listen and it sounds like lossless to me. Post below if you&#039;d disagree.

Enjoy your listening experience...
